trans-unit.source: Implements an ASP.NET handler that forwards requests to the remoting HTTP channel.
trans-unit.target: Implementerer en ASP.NET-behandlingsprogrammet som videresender kanal for ekstern kommunikasjon HTTP-forespørsler.

trans-unit.source: Custom HTTP handlers process specific, predefined types of HTTP requests.
trans-unit.target: Egendefinert HTTP-behandlingsprogrammer behandle bestemt, forhåndsdefinerte typer HTTP-forespørsler.

trans-unit.source: Executable code defined in the <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> classes, rather than conventional ASP or ASP.NET Web pages, responds to these specific requests.
trans-unit.target: Kjørbar kode som er definert i den <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>klasser, i stedet for konvensjonelt ASP eller ASP.NET Web pages, svarer på disse bestemte forespørsler.</xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>

trans-unit.source: HTTP handlers provide a way of interacting with the low-level request and response services of the IIS Web server, and provide functionality similar to ISAPI extensions but with a simpler programming model.
trans-unit.target: HTTP-behandlingsprogrammer gjør det mulig for samhandling med lavt nivå forespørselen og svar-tjenester for IIS-nettserveren, og angi funksjonalitet som til ISAPI-utvidelser, men med en enklere programming modell.

trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.Http.HttpRemotingHandler"> </xref> klasse standardverdier.

trans-unit.source: Enables processing of HTTP Web requests by the current instance.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverer behandling av HTTP-forespørsler i den gjeldende forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler.ProcessRequest%2A> methods, see <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler.ProcessRequest%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.

A <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"></xref> that provides references to the intrinsic server objects (for example, <xref uid="langword_csharp_Request" name="Request" href=""></xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_Response" name="Response" href=""></xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_Session" name="Session" href=""></xref>, and <xref uid="langword_csharp_Server" name="Server" href=""></xref>) used to service HTTP requests.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"> </xref> som inneholder referanser til de innebygde serverobjektene (for eksempel <xref uid="langword_csharp_Request" name="Request" href=""> </xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_Response" name="Response" href=""> </xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_Session" name="Session" href=""> </xref>, og <xref uid="langword_csharp_Server" name="Server" href=""> </xref>) brukes til å behandle HTTP-forespørsler.
